Brief Description:  A two player game, each player controls a jet and must
                    destroy the opponents Jet, this is accomplished when a
                    jet has been hit 75 times either by being hit by missiles
                    or air mines.


-- JOYSTICK CONTROLS --

      PORT 1 & 2:

	(UP)     =  AfterBurner only last for a couple of Seconds.

	(RIGHT)  =  Turns the Plane Right, keeping holding the
  	            Joystick in that direction.

	(LEFT)   =  Same as above but turns jet left instead.

	(DOWN)   =  Pull Back on stick to bring up the data board,
 	            which contains the following:
   	                S:  Hits on Jet
    	                A:  Ammo Remaining
               	        F:  Fuel for Afterburner
       		    To remove the board pull back on the Joystick
      		    again each player has this option as long as the
       		    Score Board part of the menu is set to USER.

	(FIRE)   =  Launch a Missile.

-- WINNING GAME --

  1)  Shoot the players jet 75 times before he gets you.

  2)  Or be the player with the lowest score (damage points)
      on his jet.

-- HINTS --

	Watch out for air mines they add 10 damage points to the jet that
        hit them score.

	When flying by or in the clouds watch out for the opponents missles
        that fly into the clouds their hard to see.

-- MENU --

		Keys    : Toggle Menu Items.

		F1      : Range of Missle:  Short Medium Long
		F2      : Air Mines      :  OFF   or    ON
		F3      : CLouds         :  OFF   or    ON
		F4      : Score Boards   :  OFF  USER   ON
		F5      : Start Game     :  Start Game
		ESC KEY : Quit           :  Current Game or Leave Game

